urs at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average of premium and interest rate components. The funding fee is exchanged between long and short position holders based on the rate sign and position size. Gate.io applies a ±0.5% funding rate cap to prevent extreme scenarios while maintaining the perpetual's tracking accuracy to LDO spot prices."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
